      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's 3am here and i'm just sitting in this tiny apartment staring at the wall. honestly sometimes i feel like if i just stopped existing tomorrow, the world wouldn't even glitch. like i'm just a ghost wandering around a city where nobody knows my name and nobody would even care if i was gone. it feels like i'm just taking up space that could be used for something else.",
